# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __getitem__, __setitem__, __delitem__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# All eighteen values are false; no decimal class implements the subscript
# access, assignment, or deletion protocols in its own __dict__.
# decimal.Decimal is a numeric type; Context is a precision/rounding
# configuration object; the exception subclasses are error types.
# None define subscript protocols.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

